snippet: The dance, which had its premiere at the Chocolate Factory in Long Island City, features “nonstopping,” or movement that never settles.
abstract: Siobhan Burke reviews premiere of Jeanine Durning dance work To Being, in which she also performs, at Chocolate Factory, Long Island City.
lead_paragraph: The dance, which had its premiere at the Chocolate Factory in Long Island City, features “nonstopping,” or movement that never settles.
